#: content/en/release-notes/krita-5-0-release-notes.md:42
msgid "Krita's resource folder used to be hardcoded. Not any more! You can now configure which folder is the resource folder and where the cache is located. Those of us who'd like to have their resource folder on a USB stick will now be able to do so."
