#. +> trunk5
#: content/en/release-notes/krita-5-0-release-notes.md:221
msgid "Docker locks have returned ([MR 623](https://invent.kde.org/graphics/krita/-/merge_requests/623))"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/en/release-notes/krita-5-0-release-notes.md:223
